title: Vegan Cake: "Converting" People in Casual Conversations.
description:
Just a bunch of anecdotes from my personal life (most of them involving veganism) in Kunming, Yunnan, China.

(Note: this was recorded in late November of 2016, when it was cold enough to wear a scarf indoors.)
